<paragraph blockId="4.[264,1325,284,1550]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[312,474,1404,1430]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Distribution:</emphasis>
Known only from the 
<typeStatus box="[770,821,1404,1430]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">type</typeStatus>
locality, floodplains of lower rio Pardo, Estado da Bahia, northeastern 
<collectingCountry box="[621,693,1444,1470]" name="Brazil" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">Brazil</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation box="[709,780,1444,1470]" captionStart="FIGURE 3" captionStartId="5.[264,368,1786,1810]" captionTargetBox="[601,986,969,1760]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[601,986,969,1760]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="FIGURE 3. Geographic distribution of species of the S. constanciae group." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/157847/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="5">
Fig. 
<number box="[764,780,1444,1470]" pageId="4" pageNumber="5" value="3.0">3</number>
</figureCitation>
).
</paragraph>
